            "id": "devotion",
            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EGod%20wants%20you%20to%20%22break%20through%22%20in%20every%20difficult%20situation%20you%20face!%20David%20faced%20his%20first%20and%20greatest%20challenge%20from%20the%20Philistines%20immediately%20after%20he%20was%20anointed%20king.%20David%20asked%20God%20if%20he%20should%20go%20out%20and%20fight%20the%20Philistines%2C%20and%20God%20instructed%20him%20to%20attack%2C%20assuring%20David%20that%20He%20would%20give%20him%20the%20victory.%20Desiring%20to%20honor%20God%20for%20answering%20his%20prayers%2C%20David%20renamed%20the%20area%20of%20battle%20so%20that%20everyone%20who%20came%20there%20in%20the%20future%20would%20know%20of%20God's%20goodness%20to%20him%20in%20that%20place.%20It%20was%20known%20as%20the%20place%20of%20breakthrough.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EDavid%20referred%20to%20the%20battle%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20innate%20power%20that%20water%20has%20to%20break%20through%20any%20resistance.%20A%20flood%20of%20waters%20is%20an%20awesome%20force.%20It%20can%20break%20down%20dams%2C%20dikes%2C%20and%20walls%2C%20even%20moving%20rocks%20as%20it%20overwhelms%20everything%20in%20its%20path.%20Even%20more%20mighty%20is%20God's%20power%2C%20a%20force%20so%20great%20that%20it%20sweeps%20away%20any%20barrier%20the%20enemy%20tries%20to%20erect%20against%20us.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ENot%20only%20is%20God%20powerful%20in%20giving%20the%20breakthrough%2C%20but%20He%20is%20also%20strategic.%20In%20the%20second%20battle%20against%20the%20Philistines%20(1%20Chronicles%2014%3A14)%2C%20God%20told%20David%20to%20encircle%20them%20and%20launch%20a%20surprise%20attack.%20David%20obeyed%20and%20broke%20through%20to%20victory%20again.%20Here%20we%20see%20that%20God%20is%20infinitely%20more%20powerful%20than%20the%20devil-and%20smarter!%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWait%20upon%20God%20for%20His%20strategy%2C%20and%20move%20at%20His%20command.%20Believe%20today%20that%20His%20power%20and%20His%20wisdom%20will%20give%20you%20a%20breakthrough%2C%20for%20He%20is%20Lord%20of%20the%20Breakthrough!%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
